links.title: Snap earnings signal an online advertising 'bonanza,' Pinterest and Twitter shares rise
links.description: Shares of tech companies in the advertising space rose Wednesday after Snap's third-quarter results signaled strength in the ad market after a difficult year because of the coronavirus pandemic.
